  <div class="pt-20 fade-in">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20 lg:py-28">
      <div class="text-xs tracking-widest-custom uppercase text-navy/60 mb-6 font-medium text-center">FAQs</div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-7xl leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-8 text-center">Frequently asked questions.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-navy/75 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Common questions owners ask before partnering with us. Have something specific? Reach out directly.</p>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">What is your fee? Do you take a percentage of my rent?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">No. We pay your agreed rent in full. Our margin comes from the guest revenue above that amount. You receive 100% of your agreed rent.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">How do you guarantee the rent?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">Leon Hospitality Group LLC signs the lease as the corporate tenant. We can provide additional guarantees, security deposits, and reserve structures depending on the agreement.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">How long do guests stay?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">Stays range from several days to several months. In jurisdictions with short-term rental regulations, we emphasize 30+ day furnished stays where required by local law. Typical guests include business travelers, traveling healthcare workers, corporate relocations, and remote professionals.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">How do you control who enters the property?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">We use platform screening, exterior cameras where permitted, electronic locks with full owner access, and direct oversight of every booking.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">How do you screen guests?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">Platform verification, government ID checks where available, booking review processes, and manual review of stay purpose. We turn down bookings that do not meet our standards.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">Which booking channels do you use?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">Primary channels include Furnished Finder, travel nurse platforms, corporate housing partners, Airbnb, VRBO, and direct booking through our own network.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">How do you prevent parties?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">Noise monitoring devices, clear and enforced house rules, screening against local guests, and fast intervention if any issue arises. We focus on business and corporate demand where party risk is structurally low.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">What insurance do you carry?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">We maintain commercial general liability coverage and a short-term rental specific policy, in addition to platform coverage. We are happy to share certificates of insurance with any owner partner before signing.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-navy/15">
          <button class="faq-button w-full flex items-center justify-between py-6 text-left gap-6">
            <span class="font-display text-xl lg:text-2xl leading-tight">What happens if the arrangement does not work out?</span>
            <svg class="faq-icon w-[22px] h-[22px] flex-shrink-0 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-content text-navy/75 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-3xl">Our leases include a mutual termination clause with reasonable notice, typically 60 to 90 days. Security deposit and reserve structures protect you even in an unexpected exit.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 text-center">
        <p class="text-navy/70 mb-6">Still have questions?</p>
        <a href="contact.html" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-navy text-cream px-8 py-4 tracking-wide hover:bg-navy-deep transition-colors">
          Contact Us
          <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

